1
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:23,920
Sigh.

2
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:24,800
There is only one month left

3
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,600
until the expo.

4
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,920
But we keep failing.

5
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,640
Let alone the new formula,

6
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,970
we can't even get the new tea leaves right.

7
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,280
Linglong.

8
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,160
I have tried almost every method

9
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,840
I can think of.

10
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:42,960
There is only the last batch of tea leaves

11
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,840
left in the withering room

12
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,079
to ferment.

13
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:46,850
If it fails again this time,

14
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,800
it means I simply have no way

15
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,640
to make better

16
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:51,120
Keemun black tea.

17
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,040
Linglong.

18
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,079
You haven't closed your eyes

19
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,320
for a whole day and night.

20
00:02:59,320 --> 00:02:59,680
Why don't you

21
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,760
take a rest first?

22
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,520
No.

23
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,440
I haven't even figured out a better method.

24
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,520
How can I

25
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,000
fall asleep?

26
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,480
But your body won't be able to take it

27
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:09,920
if you go on like this.

28
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:10,440
How about this?

29
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,200
I'll wake you up

30
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:13,400
when it's time to collect the tea later.

31
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:15,800
All right.

32
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,520
You must wake me up

33
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,579
when the time is up.

34
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,800
The tea leaves will be ruined if the time is missed.

35
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,000
Long'er.

36
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,280
I saw you sleeping soundly

37
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,680
and couldn't bear to wake you up,

38
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,800
so I came to

39
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,720
check these tea leaves for you.

40
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,360
Indeed, the time was missed.

41
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:03,960
These,

42
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,560
these tea leaves are all ruined.

43
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,160
Hmm.

44
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:07,720
No.

45
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,520
Linglong.

46
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,640
I think these tea leaves

47
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,160
are just right.

48
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,440
Long'er.

49
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,820
I came back to see you this time

50
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:19,200
because I suddenly remembered

51
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:22,800
you have studied the way of tea with me for so many years,

52
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,680
and I forgot to teach you

53
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,080
one important sentence.

54
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,160
What is it?

55
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,840
This sentence is:

56
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,320
Unintentional

57
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,920
is better than intentional.

58
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,520
Unintentional

59
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,400
is better than intentional.

60
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,600
I miss you so much.

61
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:06,160
Don't leave me here alone.

62
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,040
Father,

63
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,280
you and Mother are both gone.

64
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,520
Father.

65
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,800
I don't want to be alone.

66
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,880
Linglong.

67
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,120
Linglong,

68
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:24,980
wake up!

69
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,159
It's raining.

70
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,400
Raining?

71
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,440
The tea leaves!

72
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,200
Hurry!

73
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,360
They are really damp.

74
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,840
Go get the stove!

75
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,600
No,

76
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,960
this needs a strong fire.

77
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,680
Then fan it quickly!

78
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:12,520
Come on!

79
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,680
What is 'come on'?

80
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,920
'Come on' means cheer up.

81
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:20,000
What is pumping air?

82
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:20,720
Ah,

83
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,880
pumping air is just pumping air.

84
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:27,520
Finally done.

85
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,440
I'm exhausted.

86
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,159
Linglong,

87
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,700
smell this.

88
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,680
It has a nectar scent,

89
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,140
and some woody fragrance.

90
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,520
This is something

91
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:47,050
I've never smelled before.

92
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:48,680
Come on,

93
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,010
let's brew a cup and try.

94
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:10,240
It's an amber golden soup.

95
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,800
It looks exactly the same as the cup

96
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:14,080
you brewed at the ancestral hall tea competition.

97
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:14,760
No,

98
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,840
look closely.

99
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,920
This tea soup is more brilliant and translucent,

100
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,080
deep and rich.

101
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,200
Under the light,

102
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:22,160
there's a golden ring clinging to the cup.

103
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,480
It is an even rarer blood-amber golden soup,

104
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,410
surpassing the amber golden soup.

105
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,480
We succeeded.

106
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,680
Father,

107
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,560
is this

108
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,890
effortlessness triumphing over effort?

109
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,720
Your Excellency Ito.

110
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:48,960
Yes.

111
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,880
Your Excellency Ito.

112
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:56,480
This is the Fuji black tea we have developed.

113
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:59,040
Compared to Keemun black tea,

114
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,720
it has been improved

115
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,600
in color, aroma, and taste.

116
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,920
Mr. Ito,

117
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,960
please taste it.

118
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,640
Good tea.

119
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,400
Really good tea.

120
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,800
Congratulations, Yamamoto-san.

121
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,840
You succeeded.

122
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,280
Yes.

123
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,400
Fortunately,

124
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,440
I did not disappoint Your Excellency Ito.

125
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,440
In three days,

126
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:39,640
I will depart to attend the exhibition.

127
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,440
I believe Fuji black tea

128
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:43,520
will definitely stand out

129
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,039
at the exhibition

130
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:44,960
and

131
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,040
take the first place.

132
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,560
From now on,

133
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:51,210
when people mention black tea,

134
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,280
the first thing that comes to mind

135
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,200
will not be Keemun black tea,

136
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,240
nor Ceylon black tea,

137
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,160
but our Japanese

138
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,480
Fuji black tea.

139
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,120
Well said.

140
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,780
Yamamoto-san.

141
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,400
Yes.

142
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,840
I will return to Japan today

143
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:10,040
and wait for your good news there.

144
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:10,760
Yes.

145
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,400
Linglong.

146
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,720
I've tasted

147
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,240
your improved Keemun black tea.

148
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,320
To be honest,

149
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,970
I have been evaluating tea for over ten years,

150
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,400
and indeed,

151
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,120
it is extremely fragrant,

152
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,560
second to none.

153
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,360
I heard

154
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,680
that in three days

155
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:48,120
you will take

156
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,640
the new improved black tea

157
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,080
to the West.

158
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,760
So there is something

159
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,240
I've been thinking about.

160
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:01,440
I still had to come and tell you.

161
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:03,920
What is it?

162
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:09,720
The Hu family's tea formula

163
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,800
has most likely

164
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,600
fallen into the hands of the Japanese.

165
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,560
Why did it fall into their hands?

166
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,520
Linglong,

167
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,640
don't be anxious.

168
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:27,480
It's not that I sat back and did nothing,

169
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,560
but Yamamoto Toru

170
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:31,080
has long since fled

171
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,440
without a trace.

172
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,000
Mr. Yamamoto.

173
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,040
Speak.

174
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,120
That's impossible.

175
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:02,120
In just a few months,

176
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,800
how could Hu Linglong alone

177
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:06,680
succeed in improving it?

178
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:07,920
It's absolutely true.

179
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,480
This is the new Keemun black tea

180
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,480
our people bought from the Hu family

181
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:12,000
at a high price.

182
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:20,760
This...

183
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,520
This is Keemun black tea.

184
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,160
Yes.

185
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:25,920
Our people also found out

186
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,040
that Hu Linglong is taking her tea

187
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:28,960
to the expo.

188
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:31,440
She departs from Qimen in three days.

189
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,080
Do you think

190
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,360
our Fuji black tea

191
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,620
can compare with hers?

192
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:39,760
We absolutely cannot let Hu Linglong and her tea

193
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,080
leave Qimen.

194
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,160
Yes, sir.

195
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:42,760
Mr. Yamamoto,

196
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:43,560
leave it to me.

197
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:46,120
I'll leave this matter

198
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,360
in your hands.

199
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,640
Yes, sir.
